videos.headline: Minnesota TE wide open for short TD
videos.description: Golden Gophers TE Jake Paulson finds himself wide open for a 11-yard TD, giving Minnesota the lead 10-3.

videos.headline: Minnesota LB scoops up fumble and scores TD
videos.description: Purdue QB David Blough tries to keep it for a quarterback sneak but ends up getting stripped and Minnesota's Minn Blake Cashman returns it for a Minnesota touchdown.

videos.headline: Minnesota's Johnson makes leaping TD
videos.description: Minnesota wide receiver Tyler Johnson goes up over a defender for a leaping 12-yard touchdown.
